title: Best of The Herd
itunes:title: Best of The Herd
description:
With Colin out, Doug Gottlieb fills in to react to breaking NFL news with Russell Wilson getting a huge contract extension with Denver Broncos making him one of the highest paid players in the league. He explains what this means for Wilson and his fit in Denver, where things stand with the Seahawks now and if this have an affect on Lamar Jackson's contract negotiations. Plus, Baylor head coach Dave Aranda joins the show to tell Doug what it makes to rebuild a college football program from a 2 win season to one of the top teams in the country. 

 

#douggottliebshow
